I have seen this from a long time that im always getting less rewards in outfit with my friends and they get more even when
I am dealing more damage. In a two man outfit i get less than 50% rewards even if i deal more damage.
I testes it on a cube and i was getting like 496 uridium and my friend was getting 528.
Is this in game thing or a bug?
