On the Cube are you using SAB while the friend is using regular lasers?
The SAB does no damage and thus does not register as damage.
This is why so many people have trouble with "leachers" as they are doing damage while the main person is taking out the shields.
You are better comparing the regular NPC's instead of shared damage ones like the Cubikon.
I seem to always see a true split according to the number in the group and whether they are active in battle (attacking or being attacked) while the NPC was being killed.
